Apple has <a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2025/08/apple-hebbal-opens-this-tuesday-september-2-in-bengaluru/">previewed</a> its third retail location in India, Apple Hebbal.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/09/Apple-Hebbal-India-media-preview-Genius-Bar-and-Apple-Pickup.jpg" alt="" width="3840" height="2561" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1016479" /><br/>
The new store is located at Phoenix Mall of Asia in Bengaluru. Apple Hebbal spans approximately 8,000 square feet and is staffed by 70 employees representing 15 states across India, according to Apple. It joins Apple BKC in Mumbai and Apple Saket in Delhi.<br/>
<br/>
Apple Hebbal features a unified Genius Bar and Pickup counter, merging Apple's technical support and online order collection services into a single area. This two-in-one area has rolled out in a handful of new and renovated stores over the past year.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/09/Apple-Hebbal-India-media-preview-storefront.jpg" alt="" width="3840" height="2160" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1016480" /><br/>
To mark the occasion, Apple released a downloadable set of <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/21/apple-hebbal/">exclusive wallpapers</a> themed around the store's peacock feather-inspired design, along with a curated <a href="https://music.apple.com/in/playlist/apple-hebbal/pl.9df77b7068774e44a70c2279e064e466">Apple Music playlist</a> featuring artists from Bengaluru. The store officially opens to the public at 1 p.m. on September 2.<div class="linkback">Tags: <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/india/">India</a>, <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/retail/">Retail</a></div><br/>This article, &quot;<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/09/01/apple-previews-new-store-with-unified-counter/">Apple Previews New Store With Unified Genius Bar and Pickup Counter</a>&quot; first appeared on <a href="https://www.macrumors.com">MacRumors.com</a><br/><br/><a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/apple-previews-new-store-with-unified-genius-bar-and-pickup-counter.2464403/">Discuss this article</a> in our forums<br/><br/>